000Z","msg":"燒山五毛阿sir 正仆街！"},{"pid":"4eaba47b83ce299a9d601f096d7079123631dabe","tid":2159582,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:01:25.000Z","msg":"咩叫百害而無一弊？"},{"pid":"d44659c3710032d502cff7d7856dfe426c954068","tid":2159582,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/08/17/4RXkcP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F08%2F17%2F4RXkcP.png&h=5686e78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足為左爭取民主被拉好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以為左在囚手足 我地不惜放棄民主都要幫佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主pin this<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泛民一定要留任<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8405c2bb5561153deb0336629fcccdd8ba25c5f2","tid":2159582,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d44659c3710032d502cff7d7856dfe426c954068","tid":2159582,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/08/17/4RXkcP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F08%2F17%2F4RXkcP.png&h=5686e78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足為左爭取民主被拉好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以為左在囚手足 我地不惜放棄民主都要幫佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主pin this<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泛民一定要留任<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:54:04.000Z","msg":"眾籌幫手足，唔使靠港共份糧"},{"pid":"5a3ccd69b37bff6ecae50486c7c9d3e8f1fee64b","tid":2159582,"uid":307188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7582bbef5b6561bc2dfb35f0cd4e8eda2043ad20","tid":2159582,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tjf9YCod_gc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTjf9YCod_gc&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=5633f2b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tjf9YCod_gc</a><br />\n0:00-9:00 建制同泛民中人想延任既理據<br />\n<br />\n9:00 開始：點解泛民必須總辭<br />\n<br />\n（1）上次選舉人民只授權比你代表四年，根本無延任呢樣野。換句話說，延任就係人大委任！你接受延任，你就係承認人大委任立法會既權力，呢個先例一開，以後人大係咪可以決定埋委任邊個？接受延任就係背棄選民而依附權力，係無恥！<br />\n<br />\n（2）呼籲鍾庭耀短期內做民調，民主決定泛民是否延任。就算延任都要係人民通過民調授權，唔係共產黨話乜就乜！<br />\n<br />\n（3）依家拒絕延任係獲得國際支持既最佳時機，能對現有建制既合法性產生最大質疑，亦都會全球焦點，所有大報紙既頭條。你睇到譚耀宗，譚惠豬呢d仆街係咁放風要泛民加入，都知道北京好驚！（而如果你加入咗，就顯得建制寬容大量咁，而泛民就好低賤。香港人唔會接受呢種屈辱！）<br />\n<br />\n13:40 以後：逐點反駁支持延任既理據<br />\n<br />\n（1）由民調決定最公平，而如果邊個唔聽民意要受民意懲罰，做第二個馮檢基。<br />\n<br />\n（2）剩係留一個人在立法會負責睇文件同點人數，可以在泛民之間抽生死籌決定。（連登既共識係由公民黨DQ四子留任）<br />\n<br />\n（3）三分一關鍵少數只是修改基本法有用，其他議案包括二十三條只是簡單多數，要過就會過。你在議會根本做唔到任何事，只會被保安抬走，不斷受侮辱，侮辱你亦都係侮辱投你既選民！但如果你同十八區聯合會一齊，做真正能代表主流民意既在野代議機構，討論特區政府既每項事情，宣布真正代表香港人既官方立場，一定更有作用，犯唔到國安法，而國際傳媒就會全部聽你唔聽政府。<br />\n<br />\n（4）議員及助理人工：眾籌！市民睇你表現捐款。如果你肯辭，唔使擔心市民一定會補償你既。<br />\n<br />\n（5）下年選唔選？可選可不選，睇政府有無讓步，會唔會承諾公平選舉，唔再DQ。只有四十二人既殘缺不全既立法會唔會得到任何尊重，只會淪為笑柄。而泛民要唔要返回議會，讓議會重新獲得合法性，就係一種政治籌碼，攞翻主導權。<br />\n<br />\n（6）下屆市民一定會獎勵你大勝。<br />\n<br />\n（7）最後一點，拒絕延任係捍衛翻香港人既尊嚴。唔係你共產黨想做乜就隨便做！<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">結論：依家係總辭最佳時機，百利而無一害！</span></strong></span></p>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"泛民，總辭"},{"pid":"c2794b1356880fd0d90422f4868978423f14a421","tid":2159582,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又燈"},{"pid":"c2bf00e750c78425531b5ea7a6821b8ba6da369a","tid":2159582,"uid":292789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4eaba47b83ce299a9d601f096d7079123631dabe","tid":2159582,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:01:25.000Z","msg":"咩叫百害而無一弊？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:42:19.000Z","msg":"我都想問，但我見竟然無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪個個Reading都拎U"},{"pid":"a24b018bc366491a8c261494d172a2d92f3b60cc","tid":2159582,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2bf00e750c78425531b5ea7a6821b8ba6da369a","tid":2159582,"uid":292789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4eaba47b83ce299a9d601f096d7079123631dabe","tid":2159582,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:01:25.000Z","msg":"咩叫百害而無一弊？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:42:19.000Z","msg":"我都想問，但我見竟然無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪個個Reading都拎U"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:59:33.000Z","msg":"shit<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a4735e4e1074aed28d102c6da2d748dec2ade3","tid":2159582,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:06:38